Unfortunately, we must accept this ultimatum if we are to maintain this coalition. The Nazis and Communists are waiting in the wings for us to fail, ready to pounce upon the instability that would result from a breakup of the governing coalition.

The industrialists and small business owners are furious at our betrayal, as are a good portion of our membership throughout the factions. Our loss is the DNVP's gain, and even the NSDAP, who heavy industry see as the only people willing to stand up to the socialists.


